reviewText: This is the condensed version. The real telenovela has a BUNCH of episodes, this has 5 discs and skips some. You can still follow the story line perfectly and it was totally entertaining. I got it for a class and loved it.
this is great! the only backdrop is that the way the discs are placed inside and because of the fact that they are double discs, they get some scratches. other than that the set is great!

This novella was more than I expected. The emglish subtitles  allowed one than did not speak spanish to follow what was going on extremely well The picture clarity was exceptional. It was suggested to me by a friend in Colombia. The cost of the movie in Colombia without subtitles was way out of my price range.

Me Encanto la Version Original (Colombiana) de la Serie Sin Tetas No Hay Paraiso, estubo Muy Buena, con Maria Adelaida Puerta (Como Catalina). La Version Espaola con Amaia Salamanca (Catalina) y Miguel Angel Silvestre (El Duque), para mi fue la Mejor Adaptacion, hasta el Momento, fue Exelente tambien. La Version Telenovela llamada Sin Senos No Hay Paraiso con Carmen Villalobos tambien tubo muy buen Rating y Auge, aunque Desconosco si este Dvd es la Serie Original Colombiana o la Telenovela de Telemundo con el Nombre Censurado, ya que en Estados Unidos Tetas lo cambiaron por Pechos, cosa que me parece medio absurdo, ya que estamos en el 2011. No entiendo porque hacen eso cuando ya paso la Epoca de la Dictadura y de tanta represion, deberia de haber mas Libertad de Expresion y demas. De todas formas Ordene este Dvd, espero que sea la Serie Colombiana (Original) o la Telenovela, cualquiera sea, se que me va a Gustar, lo unico que espero es que si es la Version de Colombia contenga el Tema de Entrada Agujero, aunque le hayan modificado la Presentacion por la Palabra: Tetas/Pechos.
9/7/2011: Es la Serie Colombiana "Original", como pensaba, solo que en la Portada le Cambiaron Sin Tetas por Pechos, tambien note que en la Entrada de la Serie le Modificaron un poco el Arte del Texto, pero en sintesis es la misma Serie e Incluye la Musica Original y todo como se Transmitio en Television.
This is the original Colombian version with English subs (no Spanish subs though).  Video quality is not great, but watchable.  Maybe I am spoiled by HDTV.
ME GUSTO MUCHO ESTA VERSION, LA HISTORIA ES LA ORIGINAL Y MUY ENTRETENIDA NADA DE ABURRIDA. SI LA COMPRA NO SE ARREPENTIRA

I don't speak Spanish so I was able to follow the subtitles.  I thought it was a unique perspective.  I enjoyed seeing the outdoor scenes and the acting was great - very believable!!

WELL ACTED AND VERY REAL. DID NOT GIVE IT 5 STARS BECAUSE THE ONE LAST VIEWED IN TV WAS A LITTLE BETTER, BUT NEVERTHELESS THIS ONE WAS TRUE TO THE STORY. VERY GOOD FOR THE PRICE, GOOD QUALITY DVD'S. AS ALWAYS AMAZON GAVE ME MY MONEY'S WORTH.

THERE ARE 3 ADAPTATION OF THIS SPANISH TELENOVA, THE ONE VERSION STARRING CARMEN VILLALOBOS IS NOT ON DVD YET.THE OTHER TWO VERSION IS BOTH A MOVIE VERSION AND AN EARLIER TV SERIES.THE MISSING WITHOUT BREAST, THERE NO PARADISE STARRING CARMEN VILLALOBOS IS THE BETTER VERSION.ALL THE CHARACTER IN THE NOVEL ARE EXTENDED ON THIS VERSION,ESPECIALLY TITI,YESICA,AND PELAMBRE.WHEN THIS VERSION COMES OUT, GET IT. YOU WON'T BE DISAPPOINTED.
